                      <span>2000-06-12</span>
                    </div>
                    <span>It's just a direct "copy" of the marketing classics by the same authors "Positioning". Not many new idea there.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Good overall reflection on the present market place</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
